<plot>Bobby and Ethel keep coming up with excuses to postpone their marriage. Tired of waiting, their friends kidnap them and perform a mock marriage. Mother finds out and is shocked at the trick. She storms the hotel where they've registered as husband and wife, but Bobby surprises her by pulling out a real marriage license.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?262945</url></doc>
